data.description: Welcome to your dream home! A stunning 2021 build nestled on a corner lot with no neighbors behind. This popular Syrah floor plan is built around a courtyard, has 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an abundance of living space, wood-look plank tile and a dreamy white kitchen. Recent upgrades have elevated this home to a whole new level. The addition of shutters on all windows not only enhances the overall aesthetics but also provides privacy and light control. Other upgrades include pavers throughout the backyard, turf, a pergola, 10x12 paver pad with electrical conduit, a dog run, epoxy garage and more! Do not miss the opportunity to make this home yours.
